Text.SourceString: This dark slime thing...it's a real mess, huh?//Definitely not your ordinary enemy we're dealing with here.
Text.LocalizedString: This dark slime thing...it's a real mess, huh?//Definitely not your ordinary enemy we're dealing with here.

Text.SourceString: Everything's been upside down since this dark goop showed up. Can't wait to see it gone.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything's been upside down since this dark goop showed up. Can't wait to see it gone.

Text.SourceString: So, you're from up there, huh?//Well, buddy, trust isn't something we just hand out like souvenirs here.
Text.LocalizedString: So, you're from up there, huh?//Well, buddy, trust isn't something we just hand out like souvenirs here.

Text.SourceString: You've got quite the journey ahead to earn it.
Text.LocalizedString: You've got quite the journey ahead to earn it.

Text.SourceString: Now, now, don't be alarmed by my dashing good looks and irresistible charm.//I'm watching your every move, <Italic>pal</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Now, now, don't be alarmed by my dashing good looks and irresistible charm.//I'm watching your every move, <Italic>pal</>.

Text.SourceString: The King's orders are the King's orders, but let's be honest, your arrangement is a bit...weird, if you ask me.//Can't say it's the norm around here.
Text.LocalizedString: The King's orders are the King's orders, but let's be honest, your arrangement is a bit...weird, if you ask me.//Can't say it's the norm around here.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Princess Miranjani</> has a hunch about you.//<portrait=normal>She's got a knack for sniffing out the truth.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Princess Miranjani</> has a hunch about you.//<portrait=normal>She's got a knack for sniffing out the truth.

Text.SourceString: Change isn't exactly my cup of tea, but hey, if it's for the good of the Kingdom, I suppose I need to accept it.
Text.LocalizedString: Change isn't exactly my cup of tea, but hey, if it's for the good of the Kingdom, I suppose I need to accept it.

Text.SourceString: Your fins there...they look homemade.//You made those all on your own, I take it?
Text.LocalizedString: Your fins there...they look homemade.//You made those all on your own, I take it?

Text.SourceString: Did you bring along your fancy knick-knacks for the room, <Italic>pal</>? I'd keep a close eye on 'em if I were you.//<portrait=normal>There's a sneaky little fishy lurking around here... Mod.
Text.LocalizedString: Did you bring along your fancy knick-knacks for the room, <Italic>pal</>? I'd keep a close eye on 'em if I were you.//<portrait=normal>There's a sneaky little fishy lurking around here... Mod.

Text.SourceString: No, seriously, I have this hunch that Mod stole <NPCName>Semeru</>'s pet, Poseidon.
Text.LocalizedString: No, seriously, I have this hunch that Mod stole <NPCName>Semeru</>'s pet, Poseidon.

Text.SourceString: Ah, words, my dear friend, words. They're as cheap as dirt, you know.//It's the actions that'll truly make an impression around here. So, yeah...
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, words, my dear friend, words. They're as cheap as dirt, you know.//It's the actions that'll truly make an impression around here. So, yeah...

Text.SourceString: Ah, another day, another daring patrol. Who needs a boring old area when you can explore the great unknown?//<portrait=normal>Let's see who gets into trouble today.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, another day, another daring patrol. Who needs a boring old area when you can explore the great unknown?//<portrait=normal>Let's see who gets into trouble today.

Text.SourceString: I've got a knack for finding trouble... It's like a sixth sense, really.//<portrait=happy>So, buckle up. We're about to embark on the ride of a lifetime.
Text.LocalizedString: I've got a knack for finding trouble... It's like a sixth sense, really.//<portrait=happy>So, buckle up. We're about to embark on the ride of a lifetime.

Text.SourceString: Look who cleared Empat Pulu of that nasty stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: Look who cleared Empat Pulu of that nasty stuff.

Text.SourceString: Fine, I gotta hand it to you... Seems like you're more than just words, huh?//Keep up the good work!
Text.LocalizedString: Fine, I gotta hand it to you... Seems like you're more than just words, huh?//Keep up the good work!

Text.SourceString: You're really making things happen down there. I'm impressed.//But remember, there's a whole lot more to tackle.
Text.LocalizedString: You're really making things happen down there. I'm impressed.//But remember, there's a whole lot more to tackle.

Text.SourceString: You caught me at a bad time, <Italic>pal</>. I can't talk right now.
Text.LocalizedString: You caught me at a bad time, <Italic>pal</>. I can't talk right now.

Text.SourceString: Oh, look at the time! Gotta go now.//Stay in line, new fish!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, look at the time! Gotta go now.//Stay in line, new fish!

Text.SourceString: Hang on...was that <NPCName>Semeru</> calling my name?//I better go investigate before he starts bellowing like a grumpy sea lion.
Text.LocalizedString: Hang on...was that <NPCName>Semeru</> calling my name?//I better go investigate before he starts bellowing like a grumpy sea lion.

Text.SourceString: You think you've seen it all? Well, <Italic>pal</>, prepare to be amazed.//<portrait=normal>A whole new area's been opened. No more slimes.
Text.LocalizedString: You think you've seen it all? Well, <Italic>pal</>, prepare to be amazed.//<portrait=normal>A whole new area's been opened. No more slimes.

Text.SourceString: Great, now that Lima Pulu is cleared, <NPCName>Denali</> won't stop talking about it: "<PlayerName>$player</> is so great, awww..." *sigh*//<portrait=annoyed>Do you mind if I don't kiss you?
Text.LocalizedString: Great, now that Lima Pulu is cleared, <NPCName>Denali</> won't stop talking about it: "<PlayerName>$player</> is so great, awww..." *sigh*//<portrait=annoyed>Do you mind if I don't kiss you?

Text.SourceString: Hang on...was that <NPCName>Semeru</> calling my name?//I better go investigate before he starts bellowing like a grumpy sea lion.
Text.LocalizedString: Hang on...was that <NPCName>Semeru</> calling my name?//I better go investigate before he starts bellowing like a grumpy sea lion.

Text.SourceString: It's pouring out there, huh? Not that it makes any difference to you - you're about as drenched as the ocean itself.
Text.LocalizedString: It's pouring out there, huh? Not that it makes any difference to you - you're about as drenched as the ocean itself.

Text.SourceString: Ah, the water cycle. From cloud to ocean and back again. Just a bit of elementary knowledge from my school days.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, the water cycle. From cloud to ocean and back again. Just a bit of elementary knowledge from my school days.

Text.SourceString: Rain's just another piece of nature's machinery. Keeps the cycle turning, and the fish...well, they seem to love it.
Text.LocalizedString: Rain's just another piece of nature's machinery. Keeps the cycle turning, and the fish...well, they seem to love it.

Text.SourceString: Old tales speak of Giants who revered the rain as a gift from the divine. We might know better now, but who's to say they weren't onto something?
Text.LocalizedString: Old tales speak of Giants who revered the rain as a gift from the divine. We might know better now, but who's to say they weren't onto something?

Text.SourceString: You shouldn't be out here with the ocean all stirred up like this. It's risky for us merfolk, let alone a land-dweller like you.
Text.LocalizedString: You shouldn't be out here with the ocean all stirred up like this. It's risky for us merfolk, let alone a land-dweller like you.

Text.SourceString: If the sea decides to dance a wild tune, don't count on me to be your partner. The kingdom comes first.
Text.LocalizedString: If the sea decides to dance a wild tune, don't count on me to be your partner. The kingdom comes first.

Text.SourceString: I'll keep an eye out, that's true, but I'm not your personal lifeguard. Just...be careful, alright?
Text.LocalizedString: I'll keep an eye out, that's true, but I'm not your personal lifeguard. Just...be careful, alright?

Text.SourceString: My folks, they have a sense for these things. They say the ocean's in a foul mood. I can't help but agree.
Text.LocalizedString: My folks, they have a sense for these things. They say the ocean's in a foul mood. I can't help but agree.

Text.SourceString: Most retreat from the cold, but not me. There's something about snow drifting down to the seabed that feels...right.
Text.LocalizedString: Most retreat from the cold, but not me. There's something about snow drifting down to the seabed that feels...right.

Text.SourceString: The sea's got a chill to it, and you know what? It's invigorating. There's a certain peace that comes with the cold.
Text.LocalizedString: The sea's got a chill to it, and you know what? It's invigorating. There's a certain peace that comes with the cold.

Text.SourceString: Even the sea horses seem to have a bit more pep in their step with the cold.//<portrait=happy>It stirs something in us all, doesn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: Even the sea horses seem to have a bit more pep in their step with the cold.//<portrait=happy>It stirs something in us all, doesn't it?

Text.SourceString: Me, on guard with snowflakes drifting down? Wouldn't trade it for the world. It's when I feel most alert, most alive.
Text.LocalizedString: Me, on guard with snowflakes drifting down? Wouldn't trade it for the world. It's when I feel most alert, most alive.

Text.SourceString: Snow doesn't bother me. It's the human litter that does.//<portrait=angry>Snowflakes falling on the water should be pure, not littered with...well, litter.
Text.LocalizedString: Snow doesn't bother me. It's the human litter that does.//<portrait=angry>Snowflakes falling on the water should be pure, not littered with...well, litter.

Text.SourceString: My folks always figured I'd favor the warmer currents, being a Summer spawn and all, but turns out I'm quite the Winter fin.
Text.LocalizedString: My folks always figured I'd favor the warmer currents, being a Summer spawn and all, but turns out I'm quite the Winter fin.

Text.SourceString: I feel more myself in the cold. Denali, on the other fin, she's your true Summer merfolk – gets a bit sluggish when the water turns chilly.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel more myself in the cold. Denali, on the other fin, she's your true Summer merfolk – gets a bit sluggish when the water turns chilly.

Text.SourceString: Something's a bit fishy around here – oh, wait, that might just be me! Get it?! Half-mer joke...//<portrait=normal>Ah, anyway... So, how's your day going?
Text.LocalizedString: Something's a bit fishy around here – oh, wait, that might just be me! Get it?! Half-mer joke...//<portrait=normal>Ah, anyway... So, how's your day going?

Text.SourceString: Why are you here? You’re just going to cause trouble.
Text.LocalizedString: Why are you here? You’re just going to cause trouble.

Text.SourceString: Ha, got you! Kidding, kidding! Ease the fins, I'm not Semeru.
Text.LocalizedString: Ha, got you! Kidding, kidding! Ease the fins, I'm not Semeru.

Text.SourceString: So, what's the latest from the surface, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: So, what's the latest from the surface, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: Denali's good company on patrol, sure. She can snap like a crab when spooked, though.//<portrait=happy>A word to the wise — steer clear when she's in that tide.
Text.LocalizedString: Denali's good company on patrol, sure. She can snap like a crab when spooked, though.//<portrait=happy>A word to the wise — steer clear when she's in that tide.

Text.SourceString: Don’t tell her I said that.
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t tell her I said that.

Text.SourceString: I've got an eye for the spirals and whorls of a good shell. My collection's getting vast, might need to start cataloging them soon.
Text.LocalizedString: I've got an eye for the spirals and whorls of a good shell. My collection's getting vast, might need to start cataloging them soon.

Text.SourceString: Each shell has its own bit of the sea's song trapped inside. That's why I can't help but hoard them.//<portrait=happy>They're like...bottled echoes.
Text.LocalizedString: Each shell has its own bit of the sea's song trapped inside. That's why I can't help but hoard them.//<portrait=happy>They're like...bottled echoes.

Text.SourceString: Some say I've got too many, but what's 'too many' when it comes to the art of the ocean? You can never have enough, I say.
Text.LocalizedString: Some say I've got too many, but what's 'too many' when it comes to the art of the ocean? You can never have enough, I say.

Text.SourceString: My house is filled to the brim with shells. It's organized chaos, though — every hoarder's got their system.
Text.LocalizedString: My house is filled to the brim with shells. It's organized chaos, though — every hoarder's got their system.

Text.SourceString: Denali jokes that I'll build my own reef with all the shells I've collected. Honestly? Not a bad idea.
Text.LocalizedString: Denali jokes that I'll build my own reef with all the shells I've collected. Honestly? Not a bad idea.

Text.SourceString: Birthday twins with Denali, believe it or not. Means double the celebration, double the fun.//<portrait=concerned>She's on Summer 10th, I'm on the 8th.
Text.LocalizedString: Birthday twins with Denali, believe it or not. Means double the celebration, double the fun.//<portrait=concerned>She's on Summer 10th, I'm on the 8th.

Text.SourceString: Dang, Semeru's as grumpy as an eel with a toothache, but he's got a soft spot for that blue lobster of his. Ran away—oops.//<portrait=surprised>You didn't hear that from me.
Text.LocalizedString: Dang, Semeru's as grumpy as an eel with a toothache, but he's got a soft spot for that blue lobster of his. Ran away—oops.//<portrait=surprised>You didn't hear that from me.

Text.SourceString: If Semeru's mood was a sea storm, we'd never see calm waters. But he's the rock that guards this place, no denying that.
Text.LocalizedString: If Semeru's mood was a sea storm, we'd never see calm waters. But he's the rock that guards this place, no denying that.

Text.SourceString: Denali and I are close, more like siblings really. There's no romance there, or with anyone else around here, to be honest.//Just not on my plate right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Denali and I are close, more like siblings really. There's no romance there, or with anyone else around here, to be honest.//Just not on my plate right now.

Text.SourceString: But hey, with my looks, I'm sure I could get any fish I want. Heh heh, why? You interested?
Text.LocalizedString: But hey, with my looks, I'm sure I could get any fish I want. Heh heh, why? You interested?

Text.SourceString: Let me tell you something about patrol duty. The ocean's vast... You might wonder where one even begins or ends a patrol.//<portrait=happy>Well, the secret is this: start anywhere, stop wherever.
Text.LocalizedString: Let me tell you something about patrol duty. The ocean's vast... You might wonder where one even begins or ends a patrol.//<portrait=happy>Well, the secret is this: start anywhere, stop wherever.

Text.SourceString: It's more about keeping your eyes open at key spots than covering every inch.
Text.LocalizedString: It's more about keeping your eyes open at key spots than covering every inch.

Text.SourceString: Well, blow me down with a sea breeze, would you believe it? Rysy took that shell for her art!//My room's so full of shells, I didn't even notice one slipping away.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, blow me down with a sea breeze, would you believe it? Rysy took that shell for her art!//My room's so full of shells, I didn't even notice one slipping away.

Text.SourceString: You know, in this ocean of shells, losing one made me see the shore. Maybe it's time to stop hoarding and start appreciating, huh?//<portrait=happy>Nah, that doesn't sound like me.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, in this ocean of shells, losing one made me see the shore. Maybe it's time to stop hoarding and start appreciating, huh?//<portrait=happy>Nah, that doesn't sound like me.

Text.SourceString: Hey, <PlayerName>$Player</>, thanks for diving into this shell mystery with me.//Turns out the biggest find wasn't the shell, but realizing I might have a bit too much...well, everything!
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, <PlayerName>$Player</>, thanks for diving into this shell mystery with me.//Turns out the biggest find wasn't the shell, but realizing I might have a bit too much...well, everything!

Text.SourceString: I guess every shell has its story, and that missing one's telling me to clear some space.
Text.LocalizedString: I guess every shell has its story, and that missing one's telling me to clear some space.

Text.SourceString: So many of these shells are calling out to me!
Text.LocalizedString: So many of these shells are calling out to me!

Text.SourceString: Saw the prettiest shell the other day. Couldn't pick it up, though, because I'm running out of space to put them.
Text.LocalizedString: Saw the prettiest shell the other day. Couldn't pick it up, though, because I'm running out of space to put them.

Text.SourceString: It's either I expand my current grotto or craft a new shell sanctuary from scratch. Quite the tide to swim!
Text.LocalizedString: It's either I expand my current grotto or craft a new shell sanctuary from scratch. Quite the tide to swim!

Text.SourceString: So, you walk on dry ground all day? Must be odd not to have the sea gently swaying you.
Text.LocalizedString: So, you walk on dry ground all day? Must be odd not to have the sea gently swaying you.

Text.SourceString: Living on land sounds like a curious adventure. But don't your fins get tired of all that solid ground?//<portrait=normal>Underwater, we just glide along the currents.
Text.LocalizedString: Living on land sounds like a curious adventure. But don't your fins get tired of all that solid ground?//<portrait=normal>Underwater, we just glide along the currents.

Text.SourceString: I hear the sun can get pretty intense up there on land. Turns everything all wrinkly, like those tiny fruit snacks...what are they? Oh right, raisins!//<portrait=blushing>That's it. Raisins. I know about them. I've tried them before, yeah, buddy.
Text.LocalizedString: I hear the sun can get pretty intense up there on land. Turns everything all wrinkly, like those tiny fruit snacks...what are they? Oh right, raisins!//<portrait=blushing>That's it. Raisins. I know about them. I've tried them before, yeah, buddy.

Text.SourceString: Rysy with her tattoos, huh? It's like she paints the sea's story right on your skin.//<portrait=blushing>If I weren't so sca—ehem, fond of my scales, I might have asked for one myself.
Text.LocalizedString: Rysy with her tattoos, huh? It's like she paints the sea's story right on your skin.//<portrait=blushing>If I weren't so sca—ehem, fond of my scales, I might have asked for one myself.

Text.SourceString: Ah, the tides today are as moody as a catfish during feeding time.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, the tides today are as moody as a catfish during feeding time.

Text.SourceString: Did you see that lightning storm last night?
Text.LocalizedString: Did you see that lightning storm last night?

Text.SourceString: Did you see that lightning storm last night?
Text.LocalizedString: Did you see that lightning storm last night?

Text.SourceString: Met a dolphin pod today. Chatty bunch, always up for a race.//<portrait=happy>They think they're the sprinters of the sea, but I gave them a run for their money!
Text.LocalizedString: Met a dolphin pod today. Chatty bunch, always up for a race.//<portrait=happy>They think they're the sprinters of the sea, but I gave them a run for their money!

Text.SourceString: I swear, the octopuses around here are nosier than sea gulls at a picnic. They're always sticking their tentacles where they don't belong.
Text.LocalizedString: I swear, the octopuses around here are nosier than sea gulls at a picnic. They're always sticking their tentacles where they don't belong.

Text.SourceString: Denali told me to admire their curiosity. But no, bad advice.
Text.LocalizedString: Denali told me to admire their curiosity. But no, bad advice.

Text.SourceString: Heard a tale about a giant squid as big as a whale, guarding a sunken pirate ship. Probably just a fish tale, but who knows what lurks in the deep?
Text.LocalizedString: Heard a tale about a giant squid as big as a whale, guarding a sunken pirate ship. Probably just a fish tale, but who knows what lurks in the deep?

Text.SourceString: They say there's a melody that can calm the fiercest storm.//<portrait=concerned>I tried humming a few tunes during the last squall. Can't say it worked.
Text.LocalizedString: They say there's a melody that can calm the fiercest storm.//<portrait=concerned>I tried humming a few tunes during the last squall. Can't say it worked.

Text.SourceString: I've been trying to teach a school of fish some synchronized swimming. I don't know, I'm kind of bored, I guess.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been trying to teach a school of fish some synchronized swimming. I don't know, I'm kind of bored, I guess.

Text.SourceString: There are these underwater caves not far from here, deep and mysterious. Do you dare to go in?
Text.LocalizedString: There are these underwater caves not far from here, deep and mysterious. Do you dare to go in?

Text.SourceString: I've got to admit, I've taken a real shine to this place...having a sense of belonging is really nice, you know.//Somewhere to call home.
Text.LocalizedString: I've got to admit, I've taken a real shine to this place...having a sense of belonging is really nice, you know.//Somewhere to call home.

Text.SourceString: You see that coral cluster in front of the store? Pretty thing. It's almost as vibrant and lively as me!
Text.LocalizedString: You see that coral cluster in front of the store? Pretty thing. It's almost as vibrant and lively as me!

Text.SourceString: I'm thinking of heading up to the kelp forest, do a bit of exploring, maybe catch some rays.//I'll ask if Denali's up for a little adventure too.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm thinking of heading up to the kelp forest, do a bit of exploring, maybe catch some rays.//I'll ask if Denali's up for a little adventure too.

Text.SourceString: The dark slime thing...it was a real mess, huh? Good thing it's all in the past now.
Text.LocalizedString: The dark slime thing...it was a real mess, huh? Good thing it's all in the past now.

Text.SourceString: I've got a knack for finding trouble... It's like a sixth sense, really.//<portrait=happy>So, buckle up. We're about to embark on the ride of a lifetime.
Text.LocalizedString: I've got a knack for finding trouble... It's like a sixth sense, really.//<portrait=happy>So, buckle up. We're about to embark on the ride of a lifetime.

Text.SourceString: You caught me at a bad time, <Italic>pal</>. I can't talk right now.
Text.LocalizedString: You caught me at a bad time, <Italic>pal</>. I can't talk right now.

Text.SourceString: Hang on...was that <NPCName>Semeru</> calling my name?//I better go investigate before he starts bellowing like a grumpy sea lion.
Text.LocalizedString: Hang on...was that <NPCName>Semeru</> calling my name?//I better go investigate before he starts bellowing like a grumpy sea lion.

Text.SourceString: Good day, <PlayerName>$player</>! What brings you here?
Text.LocalizedString: Good day, <PlayerName>$player</>! What brings you here?

Text.SourceString: Hello, <PlayerName>$player</>! Keeping out of trouble, I hope?
Text.LocalizedString: Hello, <PlayerName>$player</>! Keeping out of trouble, I hope?

Text.SourceString: Hey, you! How you doing?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, you! How you doing?

Text.SourceString: So, you're a land-dweller, huh? Whats that like?
Text.LocalizedString: So, you're a land-dweller, huh? Whats that like?

Text.SourceString: Mountains and forests, huh? Sounds like a lot of dry land to me.
Text.LocalizedString: Mountains and forests, huh? Sounds like a lot of dry land to me.

Special.SourceString: I like it. We have mountains and forests instead of coral and kelp.
Special.LocalizedString: I like it. We have mountains and forests instead of coral and kelp.

Text.SourceString: Overwhelming, you say? Just wait until you've seen the depths of our kingdom. We've got overwhelming in spades down here.
Text.LocalizedString: Overwhelming, you say? Just wait until you've seen the depths of our kingdom. We've got overwhelming in spades down here.

Special.SourceString: Honestly, it's a bit overwhelming. So much to see and do above the water.
Special.LocalizedString: Honestly, it's a bit overwhelming. So much to see and do above the water.

Text.SourceString: Breathing air, huh? I suppose that's one way to live. But you're missing out on the joys of bubble-blowing contests.
Text.LocalizedString: Breathing air, huh? I suppose that's one way to live. But you're missing out on the joys of bubble-blowing contests.

Special.SourceString: It's great. Breathing air is kind of my thing.
Special.LocalizedString: It's great. Breathing air is kind of my thing.

Text.SourceString: Don't mind me, just floating through another exciting day in the kingdom. Get it? Floating?
Text.LocalizedString: Don't mind me, just floating through another exciting day in the kingdom. Get it? Floating?

Text.SourceString: I spotted a school of pufferfish earlier.//<portrait=annoyed>This situation seems a bit fishy to me. Guess it's time to dive in and see what's up.
Text.LocalizedString: I spotted a school of pufferfish earlier.//<portrait=annoyed>This situation seems a bit fishy to me. Guess it's time to dive in and see what's up.

Text.SourceString: I'd tell you a joke about the ocean, but I don't want to flounder the delivery.//<portrait=happy>Heh heh! Get it? Flounder?//<portrait=normal>Oh, come on! That was funny.
Text.LocalizedString: I'd tell you a joke about the ocean, but I don't want to flounder the delivery.//<portrait=happy>Heh heh! Get it? Flounder?//<portrait=normal>Oh, come on! That was funny.

Text.SourceString: I'd lose my own tail if it wasn't attached. Good thing I'm just guarding the gate
Text.LocalizedString: I'd lose my own tail if it wasn't attached. Good thing I'm just guarding the gate

Text.SourceString: You know, you're not as bothersome as most land-dwellers. That's almost a compliment.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, you're not as bothersome as most land-dwellers. That's almost a compliment.

Text.SourceString: I've got to admit, you've got a knack for stirring up less trouble than I expected.
Text.LocalizedString: I've got to admit, you've got a knack for stirring up less trouble than I expected.

Text.SourceString: I've been thinking, maybe not all humans are bad for the ocean.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been thinking, maybe not all humans are bad for the ocean.

Text.SourceString: You've got a good heart, <PlayerName>$player</>. It's nice having you around the kingdom.
Text.LocalizedString: You've got a good heart, <PlayerName>$player</>. It's nice having you around the kingdom.

Text.SourceString: You know, for a land-dweller, you've got quite the move. Almost merfolk-like. <Italic>Smoothhh</>.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, for a land-dweller, you've got quite the move. Almost merfolk-like. <Italic>Smoothhh</>.

Text.SourceString: Every time I pass by the gate, I see a new shell.//But duty calls, no time to clam around.
Text.LocalizedString: Every time I pass by the gate, I see a new shell.//But duty calls, no time to clam around.

Text.SourceString: Denali doesn’t get my shell fascination. Says I should focus more on the job.//<portrait=sad>Maybe she's got a point.
Text.LocalizedString: Denali doesn’t get my shell fascination. Says I should focus more on the job.//<portrait=sad>Maybe she's got a point.

Text.SourceString: Patrols with Denali are all work, no play.
Text.LocalizedString: Patrols with Denali are all work, no play.

Text.SourceString: I keep telling myself, no more shells. But then I see a real pearl, and I'm like, 'Oh, yes!'
Text.LocalizedString: I keep telling myself, no more shells. But then I see a real pearl, and I'm like, 'Oh, yes!'

Text.SourceString: I'm running out of space for my shells. But there's this one by the gate that's calling my name.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm running out of space for my shells. But there's this one by the gate that's calling my name.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, Semeru catches me eyeing shells during patrols and just shakes his head.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, Semeru catches me eyeing shells during patrols and just shakes his head.

Text.SourceString: I've gotten into trouble, don't get me wrong – many times, pal, many times.//But hey, my work's always done right, so they're cutting me some slack now.
Text.LocalizedString: I've gotten into trouble, don't get me wrong – many times, pal, many times.//But hey, my work's always done right, so they're cutting me some slack now.

Text.SourceString: You know, I saw this incredible shell on patrol. I'm going back for it later. Can't let it slip away.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, I saw this incredible shell on patrol. I'm going back for it later. Can't let it slip away.

Text.SourceString: I found a shell that reminds me of you. I'll show it to you next time you swing by.
Text.LocalizedString: I found a shell that reminds me of you. I'll show it to you next time you swing by.

Text.SourceString: I saw a purple shiny shell yesterday near the gate. Didn't take it though; it still has a snail in it. But I'm keeping my eye out.
Text.LocalizedString: I saw a purple shiny shell yesterday near the gate. Didn't take it though; it still has a snail in it. But I'm keeping my eye out.

Text.SourceString: Do you think I should go back and take the shell, let the snail live in my house?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you think I should go back and take the shell, let the snail live in my house?

Text.SourceString: It's quiet at the gate today.
Text.LocalizedString: It's quiet at the gate today.

Text.SourceString: Tried this new seaweed wrap yesterday. Delicious, but boy, did it give me a tummy ache.
Text.LocalizedString: Tried this new seaweed wrap yesterday. Delicious, but boy, did it give me a tummy ache.

Text.SourceString: Ate some coral berries last night. Tasty, but I think they were a bit too ripe. Feeling a bit gassy now.
Text.LocalizedString: Ate some coral berries last night. Tasty, but I think they were a bit too ripe. Feeling a bit gassy now.

Text.SourceString: Had the best plankton stew the other day. So good.
Text.LocalizedString: Had the best plankton stew the other day. So good.

Text.SourceString: I don't usually go for surface food, but that land-dweller snack was surprisingly good.//A bit mushy.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't usually go for surface food, but that land-dweller snack was surprisingly good.//A bit mushy.

Text.SourceString: It was the one shaped like a ball. What's it called...rice ball, I think?
Text.LocalizedString: It was the one shaped like a ball. What's it called...rice ball, I think?

Text.SourceString: Finished my shift at the gate. Time to kick back and maybe polish my shell collection.
Text.LocalizedString: Finished my shift at the gate. Time to kick back and maybe polish my shell collection.

Text.SourceString: Work's done for the day. You too, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: Work's done for the day. You too, huh?

Text.SourceString: Done guarding for the day. Maybe I'll treat myself to some kelp snacks – I've earned it.//<portrait=happy>Wanna share one?
Text.LocalizedString: Done guarding for the day. Maybe I'll treat myself to some kelp snacks – I've earned it.//<portrait=happy>Wanna share one?

Text.SourceString: Thinking about what to eat tomorrow. Maybe some plankton stew? I've had enough seaweed wraps for a week.
Text.LocalizedString: Thinking about what to eat tomorrow. Maybe some plankton stew? I've had enough seaweed wraps for a week.

Text.SourceString: Today's shift was something else. Saw a school of fish that couldn't swim straight.//Reminds me of Poseidon, Semeru's crab.
Text.LocalizedString: Today's shift was something else. Saw a school of fish that couldn't swim straight.//Reminds me of Poseidon, Semeru's crab.

Text.SourceString: After today's patrol, I'm thinking of exploring past the gate tomorrow. Might find something cool.
Text.LocalizedString: After today's patrol, I'm thinking of exploring past the gate tomorrow. Might find something cool.

Text.SourceString: The ocean's calm tonight. Makes me think about how peaceful it is down here, away from the surface world.
Text.LocalizedString: The ocean's calm tonight. Makes me think about how peaceful it is down here, away from the surface world.

Text.SourceString: I swear the water feels different every evening. Keeps life interesting, I suppose.
Text.LocalizedString: I swear the water feels different every evening. Keeps life interesting, I suppose.

Text.SourceString: Maybe I'll try cooking something new tomorrow. How hard can it be to whip up some cakes?
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I'll try cooking something new tomorrow. How hard can it be to whip up some cakes?

Text.SourceString: Patrolling's done, now for the best part of the night - doing absolutely nothing.
Text.LocalizedString: Patrolling's done, now for the best part of the night - doing absolutely nothing.

Text.SourceString: I must be part icefish – I love how the cold water tingles my scales.
Text.LocalizedString: I must be part icefish – I love how the cold water tingles my scales.

Text.SourceString: There's nothing quite like a Winter swim. It's bracing, invigorating, and just a little bit shocking – kind of like my charm, don't you think?
Text.LocalizedString: There's nothing quite like a Winter swim. It's bracing, invigorating, and just a little bit shocking – kind of like my charm, don't you think?

Text.SourceString: I might be a Summer catch, but my heart belongs in the Winter ocean.//Ah, I can't wait for the water to cool down.
Text.LocalizedString: I might be a Summer catch, but my heart belongs in the Winter ocean.//Ah, I can't wait for the water to cool down.

Text.SourceString: You've become more than just a friend to me. You're part of this ocean now.
Text.LocalizedString: You've become more than just a friend to me. You're part of this ocean now.

Text.SourceString: Thought you were after my golden shell. Guess I jumped the gun a bit there. Sorry, pal.
Text.LocalizedString: Thought you were after my golden shell. Guess I jumped the gun a bit there. Sorry, pal.

Text.SourceString: Can't be too careful these days, especially with my prized collection.
Text.LocalizedString: Can't be too careful these days, especially with my prized collection.

Text.SourceString: Denali thinks I overreacted. Maybe she's right, but you can't be too safe.
Text.LocalizedString: Denali thinks I overreacted. Maybe she's right, but you can't be too safe.

Text.SourceString: Yeah, guess you're right. Fixing this is what counts. Thanks for understanding.
Text.LocalizedString: Yeah, guess you're right. Fixing this is what counts. Thanks for understanding.

Special.SourceString: Everyone makes mistakes. What matters is you're trying to fix it.
Special.LocalizedString: Everyone makes mistakes. What matters is you're trying to fix it.

Text.SourceString: Overboard, huh? Maybe a bit. Still, better safe than sorry when it comes to my shells.
Text.LocalizedString: Overboard, huh? Maybe a bit. Still, better safe than sorry when it comes to my shells.

Special.SourceString: You did go a bit overboard. But hey, your shell, your rules.
Special.LocalizedString: You did go a bit overboard. But hey, your shell, your rules.

Text.SourceString: Exactly! You get it. When it comes to my shells, I'm not taking any chances.
Text.LocalizedString: Exactly! You get it. When it comes to my shells, I'm not taking any chances.

Special.SourceString: It's good to be cautious, especially with something so important to you.
Special.LocalizedString: It's good to be cautious, especially with something so important to you.

Text.SourceString: You're helping me find the thief now. Let's see what you're really made of.
Text.LocalizedString: You're helping me find the thief now. Let's see what you're really made of.

Text.SourceString: This thief's slippery, but they can't hide forever. Not on my watch.
Text.LocalizedString: This thief's slippery, but they can't hide forever. Not on my watch.

Text.SourceString: Questioning everyone in the square. If they know something, I'll find out.
Text.LocalizedString: Questioning everyone in the square. If they know something, I'll find out.

Text.SourceString: I have to admit, getting startled by that snail was...actually pretty funny.
Text.LocalizedString: I have to admit, getting startled by that snail was...actually pretty funny.

Text.SourceString: Next time, I'll make sure it's a shell before I get too excited. Lesson learned!
Text.LocalizedString: Next time, I'll make sure it's a shell before I get too excited. Lesson learned!

Text.SourceString: Turns out Rysy borrowed my shell. Should've guessed it wasn't really stolen.
Text.LocalizedString: Turns out Rysy borrowed my shell. Should've guessed it wasn't really stolen.

Text.SourceString: I feel a bit foolish for making such a fuss now. Glad to have the shell back, though.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel a bit foolish for making such a fuss now. Glad to have the shell back, though.

Text.SourceString: You stuck with me through this mess. I owe you one.
Text.LocalizedString: You stuck with me through this mess. I owe you one.

Text.SourceString: This whole thing made me realize...maybe I've got too many shells.
Text.LocalizedString: This whole thing made me realize...maybe I've got too many shells.

Text.SourceString: Thanks for not giving up on me, even when I was a bit...shell-shocked.
Text.LocalizedString: Thanks for not giving up on me, even when I was a bit...shell-shocked.

Text.SourceString: I've got a good feeling about this. With your help, we might just crack this.
Text.LocalizedString: I've got a good feeling about this. With your help, we might just crack this.

Text.SourceString: You've got a different way of seeing things. Might be useful in this search.
Text.LocalizedString: You've got a different way of seeing things. Might be useful in this search.

Text.SourceString: Living alone is the best. Just me, my shells, and no one else to muddy the waters.
Text.LocalizedString: Living alone is the best. Just me, my shells, and no one else to muddy the waters.

Text.SourceString: It was a bit of a swim building my grotto, but hey, totally worth it. Beats living in the barracks any day.//<portrait=surprised>No offense.
Text.LocalizedString: It was a bit of a swim building my grotto, but hey, totally worth it. Beats living in the barracks any day.//<portrait=surprised>No offense.

Text.SourceString: I've got my shells for company. They're quiet, they're pretty, and they don't ask silly questions.
Text.LocalizedString: I've got my shells for company. They're quiet, they're pretty, and they don't ask silly questions.

Text.SourceString: Patrolling the kingdom might sound grand, but it's mostly just keeping an eye on fishy characters.//<portrait=annoyed>And by fishy, I mean you.
Text.LocalizedString: Patrolling the kingdom might sound grand, but it's mostly just keeping an eye on fishy characters.//<portrait=annoyed>And by fishy, I mean you.

Text.SourceString: Ran into a curious octopus on my route. Almost tried to grab my trident! Cheeky fellow.
Text.LocalizedString: Ran into a curious octopus on my route. Almost tried to grab my trident! Cheeky fellow.

Text.SourceString: The coral is looking vibrant today. Must be the season for it.
Text.LocalizedString: The coral is looking vibrant today. Must be the season for it.

Text.SourceString: Noticed more jellyfish than usual on today's swim. Had to dodge a few stingers.
Text.LocalizedString: Noticed more jellyfish than usual on today's swim. Had to dodge a few stingers.

Text.SourceString: Found more human trash on the seabed today. When will they learn?
Text.LocalizedString: Found more human trash on the seabed today. When will they learn?

Text.SourceString: Heard a rumor about a human ship nearby. Better not be dumping their waste in our waters.
Text.LocalizedString: Heard a rumor about a human ship nearby. Better not be dumping their waste in our waters.

Text.SourceString: I keep wondering if humans will ever respect the ocean as much as we do. Seems doubtful.
Text.LocalizedString: I keep wondering if humans will ever respect the ocean as much as we do. Seems doubtful.

Text.SourceString: Water's been murky these past few days. Hard to see anything on patrol.
Text.LocalizedString: Water's been murky these past few days. Hard to see anything on patrol.

Text.SourceString: Been thinking about making a mosaic out of my shells. Could be a neat project.
Text.LocalizedString: Been thinking about making a mosaic out of my shells. Could be a neat project.

Text.SourceString: Where can I get a design, you think? Oh, I know! Rysy!
Text.LocalizedString: Where can I get a design, you think? Oh, I know! Rysy!

Text.SourceString: I sometimes explore caves when I'm not on duty. Found an interesting one last week.
Text.LocalizedString: I sometimes explore caves when I'm not on duty. Found an interesting one last week.

Text.SourceString: Had a laugh with Semeru today. He tripped over a sea cucumber – you should've seen his face!
Text.LocalizedString: Had a laugh with Semeru today. He tripped over a sea cucumber – you should've seen his face!

Text.SourceString: Oh, no. He didn't laugh. I did.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, no. He didn't laugh. I did.

Text.SourceString: I told a fish joke today. It had a great hook, but I don't think it landed well.
Text.LocalizedString: I told a fish joke today. It had a great hook, but I don't think it landed well.
